text: Rajasthan Nirman Mazdoor Sangathan (Rajasthan Construction Workers Organization) is a trade union of construction workers in Rajasthan, India. RNMS is affiliated to All India Central Council of Trade Unions. The President of RNMS is Shrilata Swaminathan. Category:All India Central Council of Trade Unions Category:Building and construction trade unions
title: Rajasthan Nirman Mazdoor Sangathan
